43:23.286 --> 43:26.186
♪ Falls on the boy's shoulder ♪

43:26.186 --> 43:28.808
♪ The journey of youth has no end ♪

43:28.808 --> 43:31.068
♪ Year by year ♪

43:32.008 --> 43:34.920
♪ Rain will pass by your window ♪

43:34.920 --> 43:37.436
♪ Then run towards the sunny day ♪

43:37.928 --> 43:40.680
♪ Dreams await at the start
of our encounter ♪

43:40.680 --> 43:42.844
