reflects in our gaze ♪

43:49.994 --> 43:51.176
♪ You smile ♪

43:51.176 --> 43:54.684
♪ And get a little closer to me ♪

43:55.688 --> 43:57.736
♪ I want to go with you ♪

43:57.736 --> 44:00.783
♪ To a farther future ♪

44:00.783 --> 44:03.272
♪ Dreams can reach the other shore ♪

44:03.272 --> 44:06.498
♪ I really like you a lot ♪

44:06.498 --> 44:09.864
♪ The first time I am brave ♪

44:09.864 --> 44:13.421
